# Demo: wts scaffold
# Usage: vhs demo-f.tape

Output demo-f.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set FontFamily "Cascadia Code"
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 150ms

Hide

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "wts f 'add gitignore for node'"
Sleep 2s
Enter

Sleep 4s

Show
Sleep 3s

# Down
# Sleep 1s
# Down
# Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 2s
